                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bowen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-12-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 16, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay instructs Mr. Bowen, in compliance with the wish of the Italian
                    Government, to afford protection to Italian subjects and interests, if agreeable
                    to the Government of Venezuela.)</p>
            </div>
